sub_title: Dutch genealogy expert and guide. Owner of Dutch Roots Explorer and Dutch Roots Tours.
summary: Hi, my name is Jan Deelstra. I'm here to research your family story or to compile a private and guided tour, designed specifically around the history of your Dutch family. You'll be surprised with what I can find about your family's past. All I have collected in my personal and professional life is applied in my companies Dutch Roots Explorer and Dutch Roots Tours: an in-depth knowledge of genealogy, analytical skills, and a passion for (family) history, culture, story telling, and people. Please visit dutchrootstour.com & dutchrootsexplorer.com
